Package: lanshare
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgl1-mesa-glx (>= 20.0) | libgl1 (>= 1.0), ca-certificates
Maintainer: gensui-fuga <gensui-fuga@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: LanShare - Cross-Platform Local Network File Sharing
 Share files across devices on your local network.
 .
 Features:
  • No internet required - works entirely on LAN
  • Web UI compatible with all devices (including iPhone 4 / iOS 7)
  • Desktop GUI with system tray (Fyne)
  • Drag & drop upload
  • Auto-discovery via mDNS
  • Cross-platform: Linux, Windows, macOS, Android, iOS
Homepage: https://github.com/gensui-fuga/lanshare
